Revision history for Game::Kezboard

0.04    2024-01-28
        Add an optional 'mulligan' button for when there is a bad hand.

0.03    2024-01-13
        And include some of the new assets.

0.02    2024-01-13
        Adjust score upwards if they start on a level after 1 (a
        lower score is better). Add a title screen and a trailing
        score screen.

0.01    2024-01-12
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
